  <brief_title>Efficacy of Celecoxib Vs Placebo to Prevent Pain in a Paced Walk</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Crossover Pilot Study of the Efficacy of Celecoxib 200 Mg Qd in Relieving Pain and Walking Dysfunction in Osteoarthritis of the Knee</official_title>
  <sponsors>
